goal: Make monica-cli dependable and agent-ready on heterogeneous self-hosted Monica installations.
objective: Convert opaque instance-side HTTP 500 failures into deterministic remediation guidance.
value: Agents can stop futile retries and hand operators the correct self-hosted fix path.
impact: Faster incident diagnosis with no credential or CRM data exposure.
outcome: Connection doctor and capability reports identify the Cloudflare proxy loader failure consistently.
why_now: The configured production instance currently exhibits this exact failure and blocks all read-only API research.
