resolution: "Added stable Cloudflare trust-proxy failure classification across raw capability probes, instance profiles, unsupported/unavailable guidance, and config doctor; expanded nullable JSON Schema validation; hardened dogfood expected-failure classification; documented operator remediation; reconciled package version to 2026.7.22."
