comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T04:43:28.254Z",codex-root,Live read-only reproduction confirmed the failure across config test and all 34 capability probes; no Monica records were modified.
  "2026-07-22T04:48:52.364Z",codex-root,"Implementation now centralizes the diagnosis in the API layer so raw capability probes, instance profiles, and config doctor share one stable contract. The built CLI reproduced the exact private-instance failure and returned the expected non-retryable diagnostic without exposing credentials."
  "2026-07-22T04:52:43.942Z",codex-root,Dogfood exposed that the read-only E2E harness treated the newly diagnosed Monica infrastructure message as an unexpected command failure even after capability probing proved the instance unhealthy. Updated the harness to classify that exact server failure as expected unavailability; write guards remain mandatory passes.
  "2026-07-22T05:03:18.119Z",codex-root,"Final actual-CLI dogfood passed 95/95 outcomes: 42 successful commands, 53 expected instance-unavailability or client-side write blocks, and 0 failures. Settings were restored at mode 0600; no Monica data mutation request was issued."
  "2026-07-22T05:04:01.156Z",codex-root,"Final verify:release correctly rejected stale package version 2026.7.21-2; today's unreleased production-ready head must use 2026.7.22. Reopened only this item to reconcile package and lockfile, then rerun all gates."
notes[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T04:43:28.254Z",codex-root,"Implementation must centralize message classification so config doctor, capability inventory, and future surfaces do not drift."
  "2026-07-22T04:48:54.400Z",codex-root,The checked-in route snapshot remains identical to upstream Monica 4.x commit 32028ce3; no new API resource family is justified. Enhancement is deliberately diagnostic rather than duplicate parity work.
learnings[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T04:43:28.254Z",codex-root,Upstream API parity can be complete while instance operability remains blocked; route coverage and server health must remain separate dimensions.
  "2026-07-22T04:48:55.709Z",codex-root,Capability probe payloads are the best canonical attachment point because downstream agent-context and instance-profile surfaces inherit the diagnosis while cached reports remain self-describing.
  "2026-07-22T05:03:18.733Z",codex-root,"The global monica executable is symlinked to this checkout, so built-source validation and actual command invocation exercised the implementation directly; bun install -g . is unnecessary for this linked development layout and reports a harmless dependency-loop error."
